Title: Secure cookie flag not being set when using HTTPS
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: omd
Date: 1751558141
Edition: cre
Level: 1
Version: 2.2.0p45

Previously the secure cookie flag was not set if the application was behind a https proxy.

With this Werk if the system apache was configured as described
<a href="https://docs.checkmk.com/latest/en/omd_https.html">here</a> the secure cookie flag is properly set
for the session cookie.
